data.title: Department of Transport and Planning
data.meta_description: Victoria’s Department of Transport and Planning (DTP) brings together key transport, planning, land, precinct and policy functions within a single department to create thriving places and connected communities.
data.text:
Together with our key agencies we are responsible for planning, building, operating, and maintaining Victoria’s transport and planning system for use by all.

Visit our Strategic Plan 2023-27: Thriving places and connected communities to learn more about our priorities.
